data.description: Welcome to 904 Jill Marie Ln, Fernley, NV 89408, where eco-friendly living blends with contemporary comfort! This modern 3-bedroom, 2-bathroom house with a 2-car garage was built in 2021 and is a true gem. Enter and notice the modern wood flooring throughout, which creates a cozy and welcoming ambiance.  A modern, gourmet kitchen that flows easily into the living areas is the focal point of the house and is ideal for hosting friends and family. Envision entertaining guests in your recently designed backyard, a secluded haven for leisure and delight. This house is unique because of its dedication to sustainability. With solar panels installed, you can save money and be more environmentally conscious while leaving a smaller environmental impact. The high-quality water softener also improves your quality of life on a daily basis.
